window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Have you ever been manipulated by friends or family? Do you want to learn how you can protect yourself from mind control and influence? Do you know what the laws of power are? Do you know how you can use mind control to influence other to do what you want them to do?</p> <p>If so, then this guide is for you. Manipulation can be good and can be bad depending on how you use it. Let’s face it; you want to learn how to read people, so you can find the right way and right technique to influence them to get what you want out of them.</p> <p>In this guide, <i>Dark Psychology &amp; 100 Techniques of Mental Manipulation: 2 Books in 1 – How to Use the Laws of Power to Influence, Persuade, and Read People</i>, you will learn:</p> <ul> <li>What is Dark Psychology</li> <li>Unmasking the Dark Persuader</li> <li>Manipulation Secrets and Tricks</li> <li>Brainwashing Techniques</li> <li>The Art of Hypnosis</li> <li>Methods to Identify Manipulation and Avoid Being a Victim</li> <li>Deception Tactics</li> <li>Powerful Mind Control Techniques to Be Aware of</li> <li>Persuasion Techniques that are Easy to Apply</li> <li>The Art of Reading People</li> <li>Why You Should Never Admit Using Manipulation</li> <li>How to Overcome Trust Issues</li> <li>How to Induce a Feeling of Overpowering Guilt</li> <li>Hide Criticism as Altruism</li> <li>The Bribery Strategy</li> <li>Creating a Scarcity Mindset</li> <li>How to Brainwash People so They Do What You Want</li> <li>How to Lead with the End in Mind</li> <li>Creating Your Manipulation Map</li> <li>How to Recognize a Manipulative Person</li> <li>And So Much More....</li> </ul> <p>Scroll up and click the “BUY” button and start learning about analyzing and understanding deception techniques that are used by all of the successful and powerful people.</p>"; 
